00:17:07.309 --> 00:17:09.990
This guy isn’t listening to me..

00:17:09.990 --> 00:17:14.411
He is just bothered about what to speak next,
how to fill the silent-gap perfectly, that

00:17:14.411 --> 00:17:15.411
